lyrics:
[Verse]
It's Glynn's birthday party, time to celebrate
Balloons and streamers all around, can't wait
Friends are gathering, in laughter we unite
Dancing and singing, it's gonna be a wild night

[Chorus]
Oh, Glynn's party, full of joy and delight
We'll dance 'til the morning, under neon lights
Jumping and grooving, with spirits high
Happy birthday, Glynn, let's make this night fly by
